      <h4 style="display: inline; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5pt;"><strong>Still Need help?</strong></h4>
      <p class="nudge-top--small">Have a question you don't see answered here? You can email us at <a href="mailto:info@heartful.ly">info@heartful.ly</a>.</p>

      <p class="nudge-top--small">For press inquiries, please contact Kate Glantz at <a href="mailto:kate@heartful.ly">kate@heartful.ly</a>.</p>

      <p class="nudge-top--small">Are you an NGO or program implementer interested in partnering with us?
For more information, visit the “Partner With Us” page of our website. You can also drop us a line at <a href="mailto:partnerships@heartful.ly">partnerships@heartful.ly</a>.</p>
